Bacon Cheeseburger

25 min
$15
650 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Cuisine:

Description

A juicy beef patty topped with crispy bacon and melted cheese, served on a toasted bun with your favorite toppings.

Ingredients

  • ground beef: 1 lb
  • bacon: 4 slices
  • cheddar cheese: 4 slices
  • burger buns: 4
  • lettuce: 1 cup
  • tomato: 1, sliced
  • onion: 1, sliced
  • pickles: 1/2 cup
  • ketchup: to taste
  • mustard: to taste
  • salt: to taste
